/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-benson-boone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-benson-boone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mark-zuckerberg-benson-boone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）分享了他打扮成本<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">森·布恩（Benson Boone）</a>的镜头，为妻子的40岁生日。</p><p> Meta Tycoon借了Boone的蓝色连身裤在生日聚会上为他的妻子Priscilla Chan博士演出。活动的录像显示，他急剧脱颖而出，像布恩（Boone）一样在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>上表演了“美丽的事物”，露出连身裤，然后在舞台上踩踏，在现场演出前表演。他还像布恩一样在钢琴上唱歌。</p><p>视频中没有使用表演中的音频，而是与Boone的最新单曲“对不起，我在这里为别人”覆盖。</p><p>扎克伯格（Zuckerberg）标记了布恩（Boone），写道：“您的妻子只有40岁！向@bensonboone喊着连身裤和新单曲。”</p><p>在下面查看： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGoDxw5PvlH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="